<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>FoodBridge Dashboard</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }

        /* Top Nav */
        .top-nav {
            background-color: #f9c8b3;
            height: 60px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 0 20px;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

            .top-nav img.logo {
                height: 30px;
            }

        /* Layout */
        .container {
            display: flex;
            height: calc(100vh - 60px);
        }

        /* Sidebar */
        .sidebar {
            width: 200px;
            background-color: white;
            border-right: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding: 20px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 25px;
        }

            .sidebar h2 {
                color: #88a06c;
                font-weight: 600;
                font-size: 18px;
            }

            .sidebar a {
                text-decoration: none;
                color: #333;
                font-size: 14px;
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                gap: 10px;
            }

        /* Main Content */
        .main-content {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 40px;
            background-color: #fdfdfd;
        }

        .profile-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .profile-info {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 15px;
        }

            .profile-info img {
                width: 60px;
                height: 60px;
                border-radius: 50%;
            }

            .profile-info .name-address {
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
            }

        .name-address h3 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .name-address p {
            margin: 2px 0;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #444;
        }

        .profile-actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
        }

            .profile-actions button {
                border: none;
                border-radius: 6px;
                padding: 8px 14px;
                font-size: 13px;
                cursor: pointer;
            }

        .request-btn {
            background-color: #d3e1d1;
            color: #2e512f;
        }

        .edit-btn {
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            color: #333;
        }

        .profile-details {
            margin-top: 30px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #fff;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #333;
        }

            .profile-details b {
                display: inline-block;
                margin-top: 15px;
            }

        .gallery {
            display: flex;
            margin-top: 20px;
            gap: 10px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

            .gallery img {
                width: 100px;
                height: 100px;
                border-radius: 8px;
                object-fit: cover;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Top Navbar -->
    <div class="top-nav">
        <img src="logo.png" alt="FoodBridge Logo" class="logo">
    </div>

    <!-- Main Container -->
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Sidebar -->
        <div class="sidebar">
            <h2>FoodBridge</h2>
            <a href="#"><img src="icon-browse.png" alt="" width="16">Browse</a>
            <a href="#"><img src="icon-requests.png" alt="" width="16">Requests</a>
            <a href="#"><img src="icon-messages.png" alt="" width="16">Messages</a>
            <a href="#"><img src="icon-history.png" alt="" width="16">History</a>
            <a href="#"><img src="icon-logout.png" alt="" width="16">Log-out</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Main Profile Content -->
        <div class="main-content">
            <div class="profile-header">
                <div class="profile-info">
                    <img src="profile-picture.jpg" alt="Profile Photo">
                    <div class="name-address">
                        <h3>Arnold Janssen Kalinga Center</h3>
                        <p>📍 2160 Visayan Avenue Brgy. 566, Sampaloc, Manila</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="profile-actions">
                    <button class="request-btn">+ Request Donation</button>
                    <button class="edit-btn">✎ Edit Profile</button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="profile-details">
                <p>St. Arnold Janssen KALINGA Center (AJKC), founded more than four years ago, continues to be a beacon of hope of Manila’s many homeless and poor people. It has welcomed within its doors many people who were neglected, abandoned and forgotten by mainstream society.</p>
                <p>KALINGA is an acronym for the programs offered by the center: Kain-Aral-LIgo-naNG-umAyos (Eat, Learn, Bathe, to be Well).</p>

                <b>OPERATING HOURS</b>
                <p>Monday to Saturday, 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM</p>

                <b>LOCATION</b>
                <p>Catholic Trade Building<br>1916 Oroquieta Road, Sta. Cruz, Manila</p>

                <b>CONTACT</b>
                <p>ajkalingafoundation@gmail.com<br>+63 961 240 8692</p>

                <div class="gallery">
                    <img src="img1.jpg" alt="Gallery 1">
                    <img src="img2.jpg" alt="Gallery 2">
                    <img src="img3.jpg" alt="Gallery 3">
                    <img src="img4.jpg" alt="Gallery 4">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
